<script>
    document.getElementById('greeting').innerHTML = "Hello Fellas, \u003ca href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/anmolsinghyadav/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #00ff41;\"\u003eAnmol\u003c/a\u003e here, and let’s dive headfirst into today’s “Hacker’s Journal”! We've got a *wild* week in the digital realm – from government networks under siege with TrueChaos and XenForo’s remote code execution disasters, to massive supply chain breaches like Axios NPM and Claude Code Leak, and a frankly alarming explosion of vulnerabilities across everything from GitHub Copilot to Cisco SD-WAN! Plus, we’re tracking targeted attacks and critical system breaks – it’s a chaotic, but undeniably *fascinating*, landscape we’re dissecting. Let’s get to it!";
